#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:7 src/window.blp:9
#: src/window.blp:20
msgid "Sudoku"
msgstr "数独"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.desktop.in:3
msgid "Solve Sudoku puzzles"
msgstr "解决数独谜题"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:8
msgid "Solve puzzles in style"
msgstr "用你的独特风格，征服每一个谜题"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:10
msgid ""
"Sudoku is a puzzle app that lets you solve classic number-placement "
"challenges. It features a clean, distraction-free design with a simple "
"interface to keep you focused and engaged."
msgstr ""
"在这款游戏中，挑战经典的数字放置谜题。它拥有简洁、无干扰的界面，让你心无旁骛"
"并乐在其中。"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:13
#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:114
msgid "Features:"
msgstr "特色："

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:15
#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:116
msgid "Modern GTK4 and libadwaita interface"
msgstr "现代的GTK4和libadwaita界面"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:16
#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:117
msgid "Keyboard shortcuts for quick access to all functions"
msgstr "快捷键支持，快速访问所有功能"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:17
#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:118
msgid "Save and load games seamlessly to continue your progress anytime"
msgstr "无缝保存和加载游戏，随时继续游玩"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:18
#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:119
msgid "Highlight active row and cell to improve focus and ease of play"
msgstr "突出显示当前行和单元格，聚焦视线，操作更加顺畅"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:19
#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:120
msgid "Conflict highlighting to help identify mistakes, ideal for beginners"
msgstr "冲突高亮提示，帮助识别错误，新手入门首选"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:20
#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:121
msgid "Suitable for all skill levels, from beginners to experts"
msgstr "适合所有技能水平，从入门级到大师级"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:27
msgid "Sudoku in light mode"
msgstr "浅色模式下的数独"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:31
msgid "Sudoku in dark mode"
msgstr "暗色模式下的数独"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:35
msgid "Sudoku landing page in dark mode"
msgstr "暗色模式下的数独首页"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:39
msgid "Sudoku landing page in light mode"
msgstr "浅色模式下的数独首页"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:56
msgid "sudoku"
msgstr "数独"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:57
msgid "puzzle"
msgstr "解谜"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:58
msgid "game"
msgstr "游戏"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:59
msgid "logic"
msgstr "逻辑"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:60
msgid "numbers"
msgstr "数字"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:71
msgid "SepehrRS"
msgstr "SepehrRS"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:78
msgid "Fixed game not being remembered after re-opening Sudoku"
msgstr "修复了重新打开数独后游戏进度未被保留的问题"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:79
msgid ""
"Also moved the Back to main menu button from the primary menu to the "
"headerbar"
msgstr "同时将返回至主菜单按钮从菜单移至标题栏"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:84
msgid "Updated completion screen and added a difficulty subtitle:"
msgstr "优化了结算界面，增加了难度标识"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:86
msgid "Completion screen now shows randomized messages with improved imagery"
msgstr "通关界面现在会展示随机消息，同时优化了相关配图"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:87
msgid "Added difficulty level as a subtitle in the header bar"
msgstr "在顶栏增加了难度等级副标题"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:93
msgid "Updated shortcuts:"
msgstr "快捷键更新："

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:95
msgid "Added F10 as primary menu's shortcut"
msgstr "增加了 F10 作为菜单快捷键"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:96
msgid "Added Ctrl + w to close Sudoku"
msgstr "增加了 Ctrl + w 来关闭数独"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:98
msgid ""
"Additionally, a logging issue when pencil mode was turned on/off is now "
"fixed."
msgstr "此外，修复了在开关候选模式时的日志记录问题。"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:103
msgid ""
"Enhanced screen reader support for Sudoku, making the game more accessible "
"and intuitive for players who rely on assistive technologies. With these "
"improvements, users can now:"
msgstr "" 
"增强的屏幕阅读器支持，让依赖辅助技术的玩家能够更便捷、更直观地体验游戏。通过这些改进"
"，用户现在可以："

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:105
msgid ""
"Receive clear feedback on whether the number they entered is correct or "
"incorrect"
msgstr "获得输入数字正误的反馈"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:106
msgid "Navigate the Sudoku interface more easily and efficiently"
msgstr "更便捷、更高效地操作数独界面"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:108
msgid "Additionally, a visual bug affecting the pencil icon has been fixed."
msgstr "此外，修复了候选模式图标显示异常的问题"

#: data/io.github.sepehr_rs.Sudoku.metainfo.xml.in:113
msgid ""
"First stable release of Sudoku! A modern GTK4/libadwaita application for "
"playing Sudoku puzzles."
msgstr "数独的第一个稳定版本！一个现代的 GTK4/libadwaita应用，游玩数独谜题"

