msgid "Sudoku Master! You've solved the puzzle with perfect logic!"
msgstr "数独大师！你以完美的逻辑解决了谜题！"

#: src/finished_overlay.py:35
msgid "Incredible! Every number found its perfect place!"
msgstr "太不可思议了！每个数字都在正确的位置！"

#: src/finished_overlay.py:36
msgid "Brilliant deduction! You've conquered this Sudoku challenge!"
msgstr "精妙的推理！你征服了这个数独挑战！"

#: src/finished_overlay.py:37
msgid "Perfect solution! Your logical thinking is outstanding!"
msgstr "完美通关！你的逻辑思维太出色了！"

#: src/finished_overlay.py:38
msgid "Amazing work! You've mastered the art of Sudoku!"
msgstr "漂亮！你已经掌握了数独的精髓！"

#: src/finished_overlay.py:39
msgid "Fantastic! Every row, column, and box is perfectly filled!"
msgstr "太棒了！每一行、每一列、每个单元格都被完美填满！"

#: src/finished_overlay.py:40
msgid "Outstanding! Your puzzle-solving skills are remarkable!"
msgstr "技惊四座！你这解谜技术令人叹服！"

#: src/finished_overlay.py:41
msgid "Excellent! You've completed the Sudoku with flying colors!"
msgstr "完美！这一关被你一举攻克！"

#: src/finished_overlay.py:42
msgid "Spectacular! Your mathematical reasoning is top-notch!"
msgstr "出神入化！你的推理能力登峰造极！"

#: src/finished_overlay.py:43
msgid "Well done! You've proven yourself a Sudoku champion!"
msgstr "好样的！你就是个当之无愧的数独高手！"

#: src/finished_overlay.py:44
msgid "Congratulations! You've solved the puzzle flawlessly!"
msgstr "恭喜！你完美地解决了这个谜题！"

#: src/finished_overlay.py:45
msgid "Victory! Your strategic thinking led to perfect completion!"
msgstr "大获全胜！运筹帷幄！完美通关！"

#: src/finished_overlay.py:46
msgid "Genius! You've mastered the Sudoku grid with precision!"
msgstr "天才！你已经掌握了数独的奥秘！"

#: src/finished_overlay.py:47
msgid "Masterpiece! Every number placement was calculated perfectly!"
msgstr "精彩绝伦！每一格都推敲得恰到好处！"

#: src/finished_overlay.py:48
msgid "Phenomenal! You've conquered this Sudoku with style!"
msgstr "神来之笔！这道数独被你轻松解开！"

