#: src/help_dialog.py:26
msgid "How to Play Sudoku"
msgstr "数独教程"

#: src/help_dialog.py:43
msgid "Welcome to Sudoku!"
msgstr "欢迎游玩数独！"

#: src/help_dialog.py:45
msgid ""
"The goal is to fill the grid so that every row, column, and 3x3 box contains "
"the numbers 1 through 9 without repeats."
msgstr "你的目标是将格子填满，使得每一行、每一列、和每个3x3宫格都包含数字1到9，且不重复。"

#: src/help_dialog.py:48
msgid "How to play:"
msgstr "游玩教程："

#: src/help_dialog.py:49
msgid "– Click on an empty cell to select it."
msgstr "- 点击空的格子来选中它。"

#: src/help_dialog.py:50
msgid "– Use your keyboard or pencil tool to input a number."
msgstr "- 使用你的键盘或者候选工具输入数字。"

#: src/help_dialog.py:51
msgid "– Use the pencil tool to make notes."
msgstr "- 使用候选模式作标记。"

#: src/help_dialog.py:52
msgid "– Use the backspace key to clear a cell."
msgstr "- 使用 backspace 清除一格。"

#: src/help_dialog.py:53
msgid "– Try to solve the puzzle logically."
msgstr "- 尝试有逻辑地解决谜题。"

#: src/help_dialog.py:55
msgid "Good luck and have fun!"
msgstr "祝你好运，玩得开心！"

